    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. RH < 1 across all five operating points confirms the CFD model is adequate to support the CPB hemolysis COU decision. The assessment team acknowledges that the rheological boundary-condition dataset (dataVintage 2025-11-03) predates the February 2026 model revision; a re-validation exercise against refreshed input data is planned for Q2 2026 and will be documented as a follow-on assessment activity. On balance, the existing evidence is judged sufficient for the current submission.",
